org.apache.distributedlog.metadata

Interface LogStreamMetadataStore

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable

    @Beta
public interface LogStreamMetadataStore
extends Closeable
    The interface to manage the log stream metadata. The implementation is responsible for creating the metadata layout.

      • getPermitManager

        PermitManager getPermitManager()
        Get the permit manager for this metadata store. It can be used for limiting the concurrent metadata operations. The implementation can disable handing over the permits when the metadata store is unavailable (for example zookeeper session expired).
        Returns:
        the permit manager
